			| Copyright  &copy; #{new Date().getFullYear()} 
			a(href='https://themeforest.net/user/pixinvent/portfolio?ref=pixinvent', target='_blank', class="text-bold-800 grey darken-2") PIXINVENT 
			|, All rights reserved. 
		span.float-md-right.d-xs-block.d-md-inline-block
			| Hand-crafted & Made with 
			i.ft-heart.pink